text: Ernst Pfister (28 April 1947 – 4 September 2022) was a German politician. He was a member of the Free Democratic Party. He was a member of the Landtag of Baden-Württemberg from 1980 to 2011. ==References== Category:1947 births Category:2022 deaths Category:Politicians from Baden-Württemberg Category:Politicians of the Free Democratic Party of Germany
